lenders.loan_because: my dear brother-in-law, Daniel Maneely, died last week and since he generously watched over many people I make these initial loans in his memory. lenders.occupational_info: My life's work involves books and children.  I have been a librarian, a bookseller and a reading addict always.  Later in the year I hope to retire and help to care for my grandchldren who live 5000 miles away, to expand their school library and to write.
